Well, you're bleeding air from the system, and in any cavity (like a wheel
cylinder) where will the air collect?  The top.

Bentley does expect you to know things like that.  It was written for
1970's mechanics.  Even the Idiot Book makes some assumptions about the
reader's knowledge level.
